<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Payment Cancellation</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            background-color: #f9fafb;
            color: #333333;
        }

        .email-container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 30px auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .email-header {
            background-color: #dc3545;
            color: #ffffff;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .email-body {
            padding: 25px 20px;
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #495057;
        }

        .email-footer {
            text-align: center;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 15px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #6c757d;
        }

        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            margin-top: 20px;
            background-color: #dc3545;
            color: #ffffff;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .button:hover {
            background-color: #da081d;
        }

        .notice {
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #6c757d;
        }

        .highlight {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #212529;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="email-container">
        <!-- Header Section -->
        <div class="email-header">
            Payment Cancellation Notice
        </div>

        <!-- Body Section -->
        <div class="email-body">
            <p>Dear <span class="highlight">{{userName}}</span>,</p>
            <p>We regret to inform you that your payment for order <span class="highlight">#{{orderId}}</span> amounting
                to <span class="highlight">{{amount}}</span> has been canceled.</p>
            <p>If this was unintentional, you can retry the payment by clicking the button below:</p>
            <a href="{{retryPaymentLink}}" class="button">Retry Payment</a>
            <p class="notice">
                If you require further assistance or have any concerns, please donâ€™t hesitate to <a
                    href="{{supportLink}}" style="color: #dc3545; text-decoration: underline;">contact our support
                    team</a>.
            </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Footer Section -->
        <div class="email-footer">
            &copy; {{year}} Your Company. All rights reserved.
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>